<topic id="how-to-exist">
  <title>How to Configure eXist Support</title>
  <body>
    <p>Follow this procedure to configure the support for an eXist database:<ol>
        <li><xref href="../tasks/configure-exist-datasource.dita#configure-exist-datasource"
            >Configure a eXist <term>Data Source</term> driver.</xref></li>
        <li><xref href="../tasks/configure-exist-connection.dita#configure-exist-connection"
            >Configure a eXist <term>Connection</term>.</xref></li>
        <li>Use the <uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol> view from the <menucascade>
            <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Show View</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol>
          </menucascade> menu or switch to the <uicontrol>Database Perspective</uicontrol>
          (available from <menucascade>
            <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Open Perspective</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Database</uicontrol>
          </menucascade>).</li>
      </ol></p>
  </body>
